descriptionHtml:
I tried to create a Charackte for Skyrim. I also created her for Oblivion long time ago. Her name: Emma Watson. Many people asked for this. I tried my best, but the tools to do this are imperfect. You can take my savegame and try to make it better. My charachter has problems with her face, if you look at her from beside/profil. This is my Creation for Oblivion: http://www.nexusmods.com/oblivion/mods/44955/?tab=3&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Foblivion%2Fajax%2Fmodimages%2F%3Fid%3D44955%26user%3D1&pUp=1.
A friend.
Files required:
-http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22903/?
-http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?

(I think thats all)
 This model is only a matrix, a kind of basic. Its not perfect. If somebody could correct or optimize (like lovely Jessica http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27955/?), please do it and load it up for everybody. Thx.
